Shell a solid.



```js
shell(data: ShellData, extrude_group: ExtrudeGroup) -> ExtrudeGroup
```

### Examples

```js
const firstSketch = startSketchOn('XY')
  |> startProfileAt([-12, 12], %)
  |> line([24, 0], %)
  |> line([0, -24], %)
  |> line([-24, 0], %)
  |> close(%)
  |> extrude(6, %)

// Remove the end face for the extrusion.
shell({ faces: ['end'], thickness: 0.25 }, firstSketch)
```
